    <h1>The Image FieldType</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-m=
acro-information">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p>FieldType identifier: <code>ezimage</code><br>Validators: File size<br>V=
alue object: <code>\eZ\Publish\Core\FieldType\Image\Value</code><span><br>A=
ssociated Services: <code><span>ezpublish.fieldType.ezimage.variation_servi=
ce</span></code></span></p>
</div>
</div>
